@host = https://localhost:5001

### Get API Status (Minimal API endpoint)
GET {{host}}/api/status

### Get Weather Forecast (Controller endpoint)
GET {{host}}/api/weatherforecast

### Health Check - All
GET {{host}}/health

### Health Check - Ready (database, storage, external APIs)
GET {{host}}/health/ready

### Health Check - Live (just app is running)
GET {{host}}/health/live
